_PAGE_UTILS_A_ORDER_BY_DESCRIPTION_: Extends lodash's orderBy with case-insensitive comparison by default while preserving all iteratee and order combinations.
_PAGE_UTILS_A_ORDER_BY_ARGUMENTS_COLLECT: Collection to iterate over (array or object).
_PAGE_UTILS_A_ORDER_BY_ARGUMENTS_ITERATE: Iteratees that define the sort criteria; accepts property paths, functions, arrays, shorthand objects, or null.
_PAGE_UTILS_A_ORDER_BY_ARGUMENTS_ORDERS_: Sort directions that correspond to iteratees (e.g., "asc", "desc"); accepts string, array, or null.
_PAGE_UTILS_A_ORDER_BY_ARGUMENTS_OPTIONS: Optional configuration object ({ caseSensitive?: boolean }) passed as the last argument.
